---
title: Striploin Steak and Creamy Mustard Pan Sauce with Garlicky Parmesan-Spinach Mash
description: Enjoy a gourmet, decadent steak dinner in the comfort of your own home. Steak is crusted with peppery Montreal Spice Blend, then seared and roasted until perfectly juicy. Ceamy potato mash, packed with Parmesan and garlic, teams up with crunchy blistered sugar snap peas to complete this all-star trio.

